item.title: Changing home telport location in project-insanity
item.dc:creator: @neil1111 neil1111
item.description:
@neil1111 wrote:

ok, go to src\server\model\players\packets and open clickingbuttons.java.

ctrl+f home teleports

you should see something like this

case 4171: case 50056: case 117048: String type = c.playerMagicBook == 0 ? "modern" : "ancient"; c.getPA().startTeleport(2315, 4555, 0, type); break;

change the c.getPA().startTeleport(2315, 4555, 0, type);
to

c.getPA().startTeleport(3088, 3501, 0, type);

that will make your home tele edge.

if you dont want edge, change 3088 and 3501 to the coords of the area you want.
